{"tid":1971233,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"sosad","createTime":"2020-04-13T18:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T04:22:17.000Z","uid":431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6bbb124b4dd59ed764e08b0d2bf4fa5b8091a084","tid":1971233,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T18:21:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟自問睇咗陶傑先生既作品都好多年<br />\n唔多唔少都學到佢嗰種高質素既英式幽默<br />\n見到咁多連登仔睇泰仔整既meme笑到碌地<br />\n我亦都唔介意露兩手俾大家睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下就係我既一個經歷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  =對方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我屌你老母!</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我知道你頭先食咗D乜嘢</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(大家一定估我會係答佢屎,但我係文明人,英式既幽默係唔會咁粗呸)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   : <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我食咩關你撚事呀?     </span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">(其實我之前嗰番說話既用意係挖個氹俾佢踩,好明顯,佢已經上釣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你頭先食咗<span style=\"color: violet;\">蕃薯</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   : <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你UP乜柒呀?</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">(依個時候<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">笑點</span></span>就嚟喇,大家注意！！！)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為你用緊把口放屁呀,哈哈</span></span><br />\n<br />\n表情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個對話同我預判到既一句都冇差<br />\n但係要去到我既境界最緊要都係多學多睇多寫<br />\n要做個木獨仔定幽默仔就要睇你努力喇<br />\n共勉之</blockquote>"},{"pid":"210abc6d4ac9c8d15d2c4d3003dd487af462872a","tid":1971233,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T18:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c6e09b9c9256e0126d026cce06268e404f4ae4","tid":1971233,"uid":203615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T18:22:05.000Z","msg":"Jm9"},{"pid":"8bcf6b0c5d888000ff8604d8a633f2edbe4d0acb","tid":1971233,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"210abc6d4ac9c8d15d2c4d3003dd487af462872a","tid":1971233,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T18:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 